snippet.title: Mario Kart 8 Deluxe – Booster Course Pass, Wave 4 hits Nintendo Switch this spring!
snippet.description:
Buy now: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-games/Mario-Kart-8-Deluxe-1173281.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=MarioKart8Deluxe%7CNDirectBCP4Announcement%7Cm_id_kg3Bbk7umA%7C1173281#Booster_Course_Pass

Wave 4 of the Mario Kart 8 Deluxe – Booster Course Pass arrives this spring. Look forward to the brand new Yoshi's Island course, as well as seeing Birdo return as a playable character!
